The map `vectorSpaceToInternalTangentSpace x` is constructed using `InternalTangentSpace.lof` which takes a pointed plot and a vector in its domain. The specific pointed plot used is `⟨⟨1, fun t ↦ x + t 0 • a⟩, ...⟩` where `a` is the vector in `X`.

